00:05:43.230 --> 00:05:45.430
A forever beautiful and powerful body.

00:05:46.270 --> 00:05:47.360
It won't age.

00:05:48.070 --> 00:05:49.070
It won't get sick.

00:05:49.550 --> 00:05:50.680
It won't be damaged.

00:05:51.120 --> 00:05:51.920
Shen Langhun,

00:05:52.659 --> 00:05:53.690
