00:06:21.180 --> 00:06:21.890
Are you okay,

00:06:21.890 --> 00:06:22.360
Shen?

00:06:23.330 --> 00:06:24.990
There's more than one of them.

00:06:36.440 --> 00:06:37.680
Kuanglan Wuxing,

00:06:38.190 --> 00:06:38.920
one of the 7 masters

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:40.460
in the battle of Tiandu Peak,

00:06:40.460 --> 00:06:42.320
is now the Fengliu Shop's lackey.

00:06:43.310 --> 00:06:45.720
Before the master,

00:06:46.600 --> 00:06:47.190
Chi Yun,

00:06:49.950 --> 00:06:51.610
how can you protect Tang Lici?

00:06:52.190 --> 00:06:53.120
A human puppet

00:06:53.430 --> 00:06:55.159
is no match for a living person!

00:07:21.790 --> 00:07:22.470
Today,

00:07:23.190 --> 00:07:23.920
with me here,

00:07:24.950 --> 00:07:26.160
you won't get past.

00:07:27.080 --> 00:07:29.480
Such touching friendship.

00:07:30.310 --> 00:07:31.430
It's unfortunate

00:07:32.159 --> 00:07:33.750
that you waste the rest of your lives

00:07:33.750 --> 00:07:35.120
for the sake of Tang Lici,

00:07:35.120 --> 00:07:36.480
the hypocrite.

00:07:38.240 --> 00:07:40.440
