00:08:33.340 --> 00:08:34.669
Are you okay, Foxy Tang?

00:08:35.030 --> 00:08:35.760
Don't worry.

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:36.909
I'm fine.

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:40.419
