00:08:44.870 --> 00:08:45.360
Chi Yun.

00:08:46.070 --> 00:08:46.800
You go ahead.

00:08:47.040 --> 00:08:48.200
Meet me at the usual place.

00:08:48.200 --> 00:08:49.200
Cut the nonsense.

00:08:50.830 --> 00:08:52.040
I'm your bodyguard.

00:08:52.900 --> 00:08:53.630
