00:14:06.320 --> 00:14:07.030
But you also know

00:14:07.030 --> 00:14:08.240
Mr. Tang is innocent.

00:14:08.630 --> 00:14:09.240
If even we

00:14:09.240 --> 00:14:10.440
don't trust Mr. Tang,

00:14:10.510 --> 00:14:11.320
then he'll truly be

00:14:11.320 --> 00:14:12.200
left all alone.

00:14:13.790 --> 00:14:15.250
Alright, I'll go with you.

00:14:15.550 --> 00:14:16.270
But Miss Shei

00:14:16.270 --> 00:14:17.680
is still at Wanqiao Chamber.

00:14:17.680 --> 00:14:18.840
I'm afraid the people from Sword King City

00:14:18.840 --> 00:14:19.550
will give her a hard time.

00:14:19.550 --> 00:14:21.010
We need to take her with us.

00:14:21.330 --> 00:14:22.330
That makes sense.

00:14:22.440 --> 00:14:22.870
Go.

00:14:23.240 --> 00:14:23.630
Go.

00:14:49.960 --> 00:14:51.690
Liu Yan used this melody before

00:14:51.830 --> 00:14:52.800
to kill me once.

00:14:54.710 --> 00:14:55.400
If he comes,

00:14:57.200 --> 00:14:58.930
I will likewise use this melody

00:14:59.120 --> 00:14:59.790
to kill him.

00:15:01.750 --> 00:15:02.600
Is that so?

00:15:04.340 --> 00:15:05.150
Well, I think

00:15:06.390 --> 00:15:07.510
