00:15:42.240 --> 00:15:43.790
whether Liu Yan will appear

00:15:44.790 --> 00:15:46.030
to save you.

00:15:48.680 --> 00:15:49.440
No.

00:15:50.480 --> 00:15:51.940
You'd better just kill me.

00:16:38.750 --> 00:16:40.550
Mr. Tang, you were indeed right.

00:16:41.960 --> 00:16:43.240
This hairpin

00:16:43.590 --> 00:16:44.630
