00:20:59.240 --> 00:21:00.000
Camellia Island imprisons

00:21:00.000 --> 00:21:01.300
all the remnants of the Jile Sect.

00:21:01.300 --> 00:21:02.480
The news of Mr. Tang's arrest warrant

00:21:02.480 --> 00:21:03.610
has already spread.

00:21:04.240 --> 00:21:05.570
If he runs into Mr. Tang,

00:21:06.270 --> 00:21:07.330
it'll be terrible.

00:21:31.350 --> 00:21:33.210
The situation is really not good.

00:21:34.550 --> 00:21:35.950
I'll ask you 3 questions.

00:21:36.830 --> 00:21:38.690
You'd better answer truthfully.

00:21:42.590 --> 00:21:43.160
I

00:21:43.920 --> 00:21:45.580
don't like being threatened.

00:21:45.640 --> 00:21:46.570
First question.

00:21:47.790 --> 00:21:48.520
Was Fang Zhou

00:21:49.510 --> 00:21:50.790
killed by you?

00:21:53.440 --> 00:21:53.880
Yes.

00:22:06.240 --> 00:22:07.400
You're very brave.

00:22:09.440 --> 00:22:11.160
Well, I'm Tang Lici after all.

00:22:11.160 --> 00:22:12.160
Second question.

00:22:12.750 --> 00:22:14.210
What is your relationship

00:22:14.640 --> 00:22:15.770
with Yique Yinyang?

00:22:16.400 --> 00:22:17.400
No relationship.

00:22:18.550 --> 00:22:19.680
Third question.

00:22:20.960 --> 00:22:21.960
Your background.

00:22:29.820 --> 00:22:30.620
Master Cheng,

00:22:31.200 --> 00:22:32.260
if you keep asking,

00:22:32.790 --> 00:22:33.400
I'm afraid

00:22:34.270 --> 00:22:35.680
I won't be able to answer.

00:22:36.410 --> 00:22:37.570
You know who I am?

00:22:38.750 --> 00:22:40.010
Dressed in blue robes.

00:22:40.570 --> 00:22:41.810
Cold as frost.

00:22:43.310 --> 00:22:44.970
With twin swords at your side.

00:22:46.200 --> 00:22:47.060
Your technique

00:22:47.550 --> 00:22:49.950
is the Heaven-Earth-Human Swords Mantra.

00:22:50.240 --> 00:22:51.240
You are the Island's Grand Judge

00:22:51.240 --> 00:22:53.030
personally appointed

00:22:53.200 --> 00:22:55.260
by Camellia Island Master Wei Beiyin

00:22:55.510 --> 00:22:56.910
and his senior disciple,

00:22:57.820 --> 00:22:59.090
Shuangjian Qihan,

00:22:59.810 --> 00:23:00.720
Cheng Yunpao.

00:23:01.550 --> 00:23:02.270
Very well.

00:23:03.880 --> 00:23:05.140
Since you know my name,

00:23:05.830 --> 00:23:07.630
you should know my personality.

00:23:08.240 --> 00:23:09.170
Camellia Island

00:23:10.030 --> 00:23:11.110
holds many followers

00:23:11.110 --> 00:23:12.510
of Yique Yinyang.

00:23:13.350 --> 00:23:15.790
They're all
under Master Cheng's supervision.

00:23:15.790 --> 00:23:16.510
I've heard

00:23:17.350 --> 00:23:19.160
Master Cheng despises evil.

00:23:20.160 --> 00:23:21.830
There's a saying in the jianghu,

00:23:21.830 --> 00:23:23.830
"Better to take a palm strike from Puzhu

00:23:23.830 --> 00:23:25.790
than face the twin swords of Camellia."

00:23:25.790 --> 00:23:27.030
Puzhu has mercy,

00:23:28.110 --> 00:23:29.070
but I don't.

