a good friend of Head Fang.

00:23:38.880 --> 00:23:39.940
If that's the case,

00:23:40.960 --> 00:23:42.640
Master Cheng should know

00:23:43.110 --> 00:23:44.440
when I met Fang Zhou,

00:23:45.000 --> 00:23:46.600
I had already lost my memory.

00:23:49.830 --> 00:23:51.430
I couldn't remember my past.

00:23:52.000 --> 00:23:53.460
Fang Zhou once wrote to me,

00:23:54.750 --> 00:23:55.830
saying he had taken in someone

00:23:55.830 --> 00:23:57.890
with golden eyes and a forehead mark.

00:24:02.640 --> 00:24:03.880
I wrote back saying,

00:24:04.380 --> 00:24:05.110
if it were me,

00:24:06.200 --> 00:24:07.800
I would never keep you alive.

00:24:08.440 --> 00:24:10.230
