00:24:10.230 --> 00:24:12.030
it's better to wrongly condemn them

00:24:12.030 --> 00:24:13.230
than let them escape.

00:24:16.640 --> 00:24:18.350
Fang Zhou once warned me

00:24:19.920 --> 00:24:22.650
never to reveal
my golden eyes and forehead mark.

00:24:23.310 --> 00:24:25.110
You should have listened to him.

00:24:28.830 --> 00:24:29.510
So,

00:24:30.110 --> 00:24:31.510
Fang Zhou was right.

00:24:32.390 --> 00:24:33.150
People

00:24:34.140 --> 00:24:36.540
only see
the golden eyes and forehead mark.

00:24:42.020 --> 00:24:44.080
Even the universally acknowledged,

00:24:44.350 --> 00:24:46.310
most upright
and incorruptible Grand Judge,

00:24:46.310 --> 00:24:47.110
Cheng Yunpao,

00:24:48.760 --> 00:24:51.620
only recognizes
the golden eyes and forehead mark.

